/*
 * mps3/corstone300/an547 overlay for pse84_assistant — QEMU Cortex-M55
 * smoke-test build.
 *
 * Intentionally empty: the upstream board DTS already provides uart0 as
 * zephyr,console, NVIC, systick, and the MPS3 memory map (ITCM flash /
 * DTCM SRAM). We deliberately do NOT declare a zephyr,display or
 * gpio-keys node here — the QEMU model has no panel or buttons, and
 * the headless build path in src/main.c (CONFIG_LVGL=n) drives state
 * transitions from a k_timer instead.
 *
 * If the upstream board ever starts auto-enabling a display controller
 * we do not want, suppress it here with `status = "disabled"`.
 */
